00:40:22,719 --> 00:40:36,719
A lot of people have asked me about that and think because I was Bill's good friend for so many years that I knew more than the snippets that he published here and there about community.

231
00:40:36,719 --> 00:40:49,719
But community and democracy were the small D. And pretty much everything it's in is writing. There's nothing hidden anywhere else.

232
00:40:49,719 --> 00:40:57,719
It's kind of an exploration of ideas. I think that he was interested in.

